    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "The quality of teaching at Master School Of Management is very good. The college is blessed with a wonderful set of faculties who impart quality education to the students.",
        "Yes, colleges pre-internship training has proven to be the best way to prepare students for the industry.",
        "The college has an excellent placement team, with a very good percentage of students getting placed every year.",
        "Financial assistance is the best, and the campus jobs are excellent. Students have the opportunity to work in big companies like Kangaroo, Timcon, etc.",
